# <type>(<scope>): <imperative description, ≤72 chars, no trailing period>
#
# Body (optional): explain the WHY, not the what. Wrap at ~72 columns.
#
# Footer (optional): BREAKING CHANGE: ... | Refs #123
#
# ── types ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   feat      new public functionality
#   fix       bug fix
#   refactor  internal change without altering behavior
#   perf      performance improvement
#   docs      README, JSDoc, examples
#   test      adds/adjusts tests
#   build     build, packaging, package.json, tsconfig
#   chore     auxiliary tasks (deps, configs)
#
# ── scopes ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   core:        result | task | context
#   combinators: parallel | pipe | fallback | race
#   middleware:  retry | timeout | cache | circuit-breaker
#   others:      index | examples | deps
#
# e.g.: fix(retry): convert abort during the wait into Err instead of throwing
